data.eml:eml: A new species of Sycorax Curtis (Diptera, Psychodidae, Sycoracinae) collected on harlequin frogs (Anura: Bufonidae, Atelopus) in the Ecuadorian Andes

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bravo, Freddy, Salazar-Valenzuela, David (2009): A new species of Sycorax Curtis (Diptera, Psychodidae, Sycoracinae) collected on harlequin frogs (Anura: Bufonidae, Atelopus) in the Ecuadorian Andes. Zootaxa 2093: 37-42, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.187566
